Description: Rest on the flight into Egypt; the Virgin dips a bowl into a pool of water as Joseph and Jesus play with a tree branch with berries; the donkey stands at right. 1575 Engraving
Curator's comments: After a painting by Barocci known through several versions, see A. Emiliani, 'Federico Barocci', 1985, volume I, pages 78-85; related painting, dated 1573, in the Vatican. Hollstein describes an extraordinary number of copies from a-p (ie, 16). Hollstein calls this print "Rest on the return from Egypt".
